I"ø<p>Semaphore is a cross-domain, multi-modal and experimental entertainment by <a href="http://rhoadley.net/">Richard Hoadley</a>, <a href="https://www.essex.ac.uk/people/TERRY17202/philip-arthur-terry">Phil Terry</a>, <a href="http://janeturner.net/">Jane Turner</a>. The Microsoft Kinect maps dance movements to trigger and modulate text, sound synthesis and musical notation. Me? I only recorded the video and edited this short film below for Richard.</p>

